headline: Raymond James Ltd. Expands into Manitoba with the Acquisition of Three Leading Winnipeg Teams bringing over $1B in client assets
summary: Raymond James Ltd., Canada's largest independent financial services firm, is proud to announce the decision of three distinguished Winnipeg-based teams to join the firm. Managing over $1B in client assets, Martin Wealth Management, Miles Wealth Management Group, and Ruban Stark Wealth Partners will anchor the opening of a new Raymond James office in Winnipeg.
